  gift: `<polyline points="20 12 20 22 4 22 4 12"/><rect width="20" height="5" x="2" y="7" rx="1"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="22" y2="7"/><path d="M12 7H7.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5C11 2 12 7 12 7zM12 7h4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5C13 2 12 7 12 7z"/>`,

